---
source: tests/cli.rs
expression: "help_output(& [\"git\", \"--help\"])"
---
Git helpers: sensible defaults and global ignore vaccination

Usage: hpds git [OPTIONS] <COMMAND>

Commands:
  setup      Configure sensible git defaults and gh auth guidance
  vaccinate  Add R/Python/editor junk patterns to the global git ignore
  help       Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -v, --verbose        Show more detail (underlying commands, tool names)
  -q, --quiet          Suppress all output except errors
      --no-color       Disable colored output
      --config <PATH>  Use this config file instead of discovering hpds.toml
  -h, --help           Print help
